1
00:00:05,043 --> 00:00:07,912
I want you to get rid of that family.

2
00:00:09,080 --> 00:00:12,117
What do you mean "get rid of"?

3
00:00:12,684 --> 00:00:14,085
<i>The Tagusari family…</i>

4
00:00:14,853 --> 00:00:16,321
<i>Kill them all for me.</i>

5
00:00:19,290 --> 00:00:22,927
<i>Mogi regretted it the entire time.</i>

6
00:00:23,728 --> 00:00:26,197
If only back then, I had stopped him…

7
00:00:26,264 --> 00:00:27,132
That's enough.

8
00:00:27,699 --> 00:00:29,701
Wait, I'm still talking--

9
00:00:29,767 --> 00:00:31,636
I've waited 31 years.

10
00:00:31,703 --> 00:00:33,304
That's more than enough.

11
00:00:41,279 --> 00:00:42,480
Makoto.

12
00:00:43,448 --> 00:00:44,782
Let me kill him.

13
00:00:47,519 --> 00:00:49,087
They didn't run away!

14
00:00:50,955 --> 00:00:52,390
They didn't even move.

15
00:00:53,892 --> 00:00:55,460
Sakutaro and Yuka…

16
00:00:55,527 --> 00:00:57,195
They didn't even make a sound.

17
00:00:59,497 --> 00:01:00,965
That's what Mogi said.

18
00:01:06,204 --> 00:01:08,606
What are you talking about?
Don't mess with us!

19
00:01:10,475 --> 00:01:11,743
Could it be…

20
00:01:14,846 --> 00:01:16,314
They were already dead?

21
00:01:18,449 --> 00:01:20,051
You too? What are you going on about?

22
00:01:24,656 --> 00:01:25,657
Minoru!

23
00:01:44,409 --> 00:01:45,543
Why did you stop?

24
00:01:48,112 --> 00:01:49,847
She's obviously just bullshitting!

25
00:01:51,182 --> 00:01:53,151
It's true there's no proof.

26
00:01:53,851 --> 00:01:56,955
But there's no proof our parents
were alive back then, either.

27
00:01:57,555 --> 00:01:59,524
You're really going to believe that story?

28
00:02:00,258 --> 00:02:02,360
You can't get revenge
based on speculation.

29
00:02:02,427 --> 00:02:04,195
Mogi is the killer!

30
00:02:04,262 --> 00:02:05,263
But…

31
00:02:05,330 --> 00:02:07,932
If the story is true,
there's a new culprit out there.

32
00:02:10,201 --> 00:02:11,236
Minoru.

33
00:02:11,302 --> 00:02:13,905
That would mean Mogi isn't the killer.

34
00:02:14,806 --> 00:02:17,141
So I have to look into it.

35
00:02:37,161 --> 00:02:40,198
<i>Just what on earth are you hiding?</i>

36
00:02:41,099 --> 00:02:43,301
<i>Haruko Ashikaga.</i>

37
00:02:58,216 --> 00:03:00,418
I'll go check
the remaining people involved.

38
00:03:03,354 --> 00:03:07,325
The ones who ordered Mogi to murder them
were the factory manager and Sasaoka.

39
00:03:08,393 --> 00:03:11,329
Amagi from the Igarashi-gumi
might be involved too.

40
00:03:11,829 --> 00:03:13,564
And also Mr. Koike.

